  "detailed_description": "<strong>Saikyo Robots</strong> combines real time strategy and roguelike. <br>Daytimes are calm. Command your army, grow it, gather resources and explore.<br>Upgrade your base and army to create the strongest robot army there is! Why? <br>Because the cloud king will attack your base every night!<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2428750/extras/c2183b174cfd4e30fb3facc3cd789f86.avif?t=1732691323\" width=608 height=84 /></span> <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2428750/extras/adfa405d77b893545fcdd86a7aa7d3fa.poster.avif?t=1732691323\" width=608 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2428750/extras/adfa405d77b893545fcdd86a7aa7d3fa.webm?t=1732691323\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2428750/extras/adfa405d77b893545fcdd86a7aa7d3fa.mp4?t=1732691323\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Robots follow your command to fight, collect, repair and build. Lead your army wisely!<br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2428750/extras/d349a3765028c4c3a207147ab7164f99.avif?t=1732691323\" width=608 height=84 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2428750/extras/c102c1292bc8ef3c8e961bcaf4f6cd8d.poster.avif?t=1732691323\" width=608 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2428750/extras/c102c1292bc8ef3c8e961bcaf4f6cd8d.webm?t=1732691323\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2428750/extras/c102c1292bc8ef3c8e961bcaf4f6cd8d.mp4?t=1732691323\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Each level has resources, hidden upgrades, enemies and lost robots. Explore each level to find them all!<br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2428750/extras/b6266563d06b879559acaf31265ce192.avif?t=1732691323\" width=608 height=84 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2428750/extras/b275149de4ce7d3e986e792080121fd7.poster.avif?t=1732691323\" width=608 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2428750/extras/b275149de4ce7d3e986e792080121fd7.webm?t=1732691323\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2428750/extras/b275149de4ce7d3e986e792080121fd7.mp4?t=1732691323\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Choose upgrades from over 50 different ones. Each day stronger upgrades become available<br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2428750/extras/bc5a28cab7b2663455324f7adbe86d29.avif?t=1732691323\" width=608 height=84 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2428750/extras/45bffdf7a07d4a1183049a25616c92ac.poster.avif?t=1732691323\" width=608 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2428750/extras/45bffdf7a07d4a1183049a25616c92ac.webm?t=1732691323\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2428750/extras/45bffdf7a07d4a1183049a25616c92ac.mp4?t=1732691323\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Survive the nightly attacks from the cloud king's army. They come out of nowhere ... there must be a way to fight back!",
  "about_the_game": "<strong>Saikyo Robots</strong> combines real time strategy and roguelike. <br>Daytimes are calm. Command your army, grow it, gather resources and explore.<br>Upgrade your base and army to create the strongest robot army there is! Why? <br>Because the cloud king will attack your base every night!<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2428750/extras/c2183b174cfd4e30fb3facc3cd789f86.avif?t=1732691323\" width=608 height=84 /></span> <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2428750/extras/adfa405d77b893545fcdd86a7aa7d3fa.poster.avif?t=1732691323\" width=608 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2428750/extras/adfa405d77b893545fcdd86a7aa7d3fa.webm?t=1732691323\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2428750/extras/adfa405d77b893545fcdd86a7aa7d3fa.mp4?t=1732691323\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Robots follow your command to fight, collect, repair and build. Lead your army wisely!<br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2428750/extras/d349a3765028c4c3a207147ab7164f99.avif?t=1732691323\" width=608 height=84 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2428750/extras/c102c1292bc8ef3c8e961bcaf4f6cd8d.poster.avif?t=1732691323\" width=608 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2428750/extras/c102c1292bc8ef3c8e961bcaf4f6cd8d.webm?t=1732691323\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2428750/extras/c102c1292bc8ef3c8e961bcaf4f6cd8d.mp4?t=1732691323\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Each level has resources, hidden upgrades, enemies and lost robots. Explore each level to find them all!<br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2428750/extras/b6266563d06b879559acaf31265ce192.avif?t=1732691323\" width=608 height=84 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2428750/extras/b275149de4ce7d3e986e792080121fd7.poster.avif?t=1732691323\" width=608 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2428750/extras/b275149de4ce7d3e986e792080121fd7.webm?t=1732691323\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2428750/extras/b275149de4ce7d3e986e792080121fd7.mp4?t=1732691323\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Choose upgrades from over 50 different ones. Each day stronger upgrades become available<br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2428750/extras/bc5a28cab7b2663455324f7adbe86d29.avif?t=1732691323\" width=608 height=84 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2428750/extras/45bffdf7a07d4a1183049a25616c92ac.poster.avif?t=1732691323\" width=608 height=342 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2428750/extras/45bffdf7a07d4a1183049a25616c92ac.webm?t=1732691323\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2428750/extras/45bffdf7a07d4a1183049a25616c92ac.m